Package: libmidas-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libmidas-1.1-2 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: quick port of the MIDAS Digital Audio System to SDL
 MIDAS Digital Audio System is a multichannel digital sound and music
 system, designed mainly for use in games, demos, and other realtime
 multimedia applications. MIDAS is free for non-commercial usage, but
 licenses for commercial use are also available. 

